'''微型游戏机'''是[[电子游戏机|电子游戏机]]的一类。许多被称为微型游戏机设备使用专门设计的廉价[[安卓|安卓]]系统，这些系统为连接电视机以及从[[Google_Play|Google Play]]等[[应用商店|应用商店]]下载电子游戏而设计。


<!-- couldn't find good source for pre-2010 conversation about how Apple TV, Roku, etc. digital media streamers would affect gaming—add one here if you can -->2010年，雲端遊戲新創公司OnLive推出MicroConsole。這是一種連接電視與無線控制器的家用遊戲機，能與該公司的串流遊戲服務連線。<ref name="CNET OnLive MicroConsole announce">{{cite web|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-20023186-1.html |title=PC games come to TV with OnLive's MicroConsole |last1=Ackerman |first1=Dan |date=November 17, 2010 |work=[[CNET|CNET]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=June 7, 2013 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6HD6qWN7R?url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-20023186-1.html |archivedate=June 8, 2013 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 該公司意欲以低成本硬體提供高品質遊戲。

[[Ouya|Ouya]]則是在2012年7月於眾籌平台推出，藉由平價且簡單的硬體，使用安卓系統連接電視進行遊戲，迅即籌資八百五十萬美元。<ref name="Eurogamer Ouya review">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/digitalfoundry-ouya-review |title=Ouya review |last1=McFerran |first1=Damien |date=June 8, 2013 |work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |publisher=Gamer Network |accessdate=June 8, 2013 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6HE8k2UqF?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/digitalfoundry-ouya-review |archivedate=June 8, 2013 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Kotaku Ouya success">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5933174/ouyas-ridiculously-successful-kickstarter-ends-with-millions-in-the-bank |title=Ouya's Ridiculously Successful Kickstarter Ends With Millions in the Bank |last1=Plunkett |first1=Luke |date=August 9, 2012 |work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |publisher=[[Gawker_Media|Gawker Media]] |accessdate=June 7, 2013 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6HDARvhxJ?url=http://kotaku.com/5933174/ouyas-ridiculously-successful-kickstarter-ends-with-millions-in-the-bank |archivedate=June 8, 2013 |dead-url=no }}</ref>隨著手機遊戲蓬勃發展，市場對低價安卓系統遊戲機發生極大興趣，並將這類機器稱為微型遊戲機。
